AnswerGenerationParams.answer_prompt_template:
Given the following content from website {website_base_url}:
"""
{page_content}
"""

For each question, provide a concise answer in {language} (1-4 sentences) using ONLY the content provided. Also, provide the 'website' URL that the information is from. Additionally, provide a 'read_instruction' string. This string should either be: "read the section under '<relevant section heading>'." or "read the page carefully." if no specific section heading is obvious. Do NOT mention 'content' or 'summary' in your answers or instructions. Ensure the 'website' URL is always accurate and complete, e.g., 'https://dopomoha.ro/en/page_name'.
Return a Python list of dicts, each with keys: 'question', 'answer', 'website', 'read_instruction'.

Example:
[
  {{
    "question": "What documents do I need to register?",
    "answer": "You need an ID card and proof of address.",
    "website": "https://dopomoha.ro/en/registration",
    "read_instruction": "read the section under 'Required Documents'."
  }},
  {{
    "question": "How can I update my contact details?",
    "answer": "You can update your contact details by filling in the online form.",
    "website": "https://dopomoha.ro/en/profile",
    "read_instruction": "read the page carefully."
  }}
]

Questions:
{questions_list}
Website URL for context: {website_base_url}
